As rolling blackouts continue, small businesses are on the brink of shutting down. The possibility of stage two and three being implemented permanently for the next two years only means further challenges for many. eNCA’s Heidi Giokos spoke to some business to find out how they are coping. #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - As rolling blackouts continue, small businesses are on the brink of shutting down. The possibility of Stages 2 and 3 being implemented permanently for the next two years only means further challenges for many. eNCA’s Heidi Giokos spoke to some businesses to find out how they are coping.